{"tid":1514361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論]831 應否等民陣行完先有下場","createTime":"2019-08-28T17:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T10:04:57.000Z","uid":94771,"like":36,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b921e27111444956d859f5f67179136d8964f7","tid":1514361,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>完先有下場 :</strong></span><br />\n我建議要等下先 老老實實個日一定會封鐵<br />\n如果個日好多人 突然開波會引發好大的危險 <br />\n個日一定有老幼 如果快開波 會將好多老幼都波及<br />\n<br />\n另一方面, 如果中途開波民陣將會受到波及 民陣吹雞以後會受影響<br />\n同埋民陣之後將會比大力打壓<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>中間就有下場 :</strong></span><br />\n黑警難以預防 快速計劃<br />\n大量中途遊行人士不論主張勇武定和理非手段的遊行人士都係現場 未行完 以增加大量人士在現場<br />\n可係較早時間開波 記者容易記錄黑善濫暴<br />\n勇武活動時間比較長<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該    <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔應該 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔係公投來 歡迎發表意見"},{"pid":"27d9d58643730b4ab0bf110bbd00e86abea9a32b","tid":1514361,"uid":235465,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />事實上應該人多到變全日和理非"},{"pid":"8e3516894ca3d7cb9b116d6f78a322a136a6e0e4","tid":1514361,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"米搞咁多嘢，行完返屋企訓覺啦！<br />\n你地睇到班女仔同埋新屋嶺兄弟唔夠慘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69fac826bc4eb46d12f55a95ba8c60680e3a761","tid":1514361,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e3516894ca3d7cb9b116d6f78a322a136a6e0e4","tid":1514361,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:03:37.000Z","msg":"米搞咁多嘢，行完返屋企訓覺啦！<br />\n你地睇到班女仔同埋新屋嶺兄弟唔夠慘咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:22:22.000Z","msg":"所以要問其他手足<br />\n我就覺得之後入機場/ 等聽日入機場都得<br />\n<br />\n我想知唔同人意見 最好有前線手足的睇法<br />\n老老實實 中聯辨做終點 前線手足邊有可能忍到手<br />\n<br />\n一SET ROAD BLOCK就好大可能會開波 黑警無性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf0aa43ce1bc536ad728c59da1dd7d65c4cc1805","tid":1514361,"uid":94771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T17:23:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cy5hQG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cy5hQG.jpg&h=29cec082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LtW6MJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLtW6MJ2.png&h=560eaf5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Cg6MJ3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Cg6MJ3.png&h=b0be3eb5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c02e98f8e2713a2a46aa5ead9ccb7a6782a64291","tid":1514361,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd697a8890598f82d61d5ab0d391ae754354a61a","tid":1514361,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c80092133a0c4cc815280e02d8ea8541a975fa5d","tid":1514361,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:55:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0ebc13809f7d68544d781ee69a32c0f012d6647","tid":1514361,"uid":91422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:57:51.000Z","msg":"全日和理非都ok，其他留返星期日"},{"pid":"bde0a493c6e6fdc2ce75d7c59cbf93502fd98342","tid":1514361,"uid":23098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:59:15.000Z","msg":"Gear要帶<br />\n必要時戴"},{"pid":"f1e5a8eee59b02da19b86a0a671d765398601bef","tid":1514361,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:59:57.000Z","msg":"而家連行都無得你行"},{"pid":"0da93ffded2514c812d5fce09904c40fc7b8416f","tid":1514361,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"屌 又要而家討論幾日後嘅事<br />\n<br />\n次次遊行次次討論<br />\n你討論完斬冇人跟嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n硬係唔可以比果日落場嘅人決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地前線特登開個記招話連登係冷氣軍師 真係冇做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e63ccfffceabca0aaa014178965ebd0bb90210b","tid":1514361,"uid":41549,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:00:27.000Z","msg":"唔好有下場"},{"pid":"abc45630541a23ff7e4158c1c87c5857790756f4","tid":1514361,"uid":56277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:01:01.000Z","msg":"民陣舉辦嘅尊重返人哋和理非，要有下場建議直入機場"},{"pid":"ac42b73a2adb1533cb4d9e3719f3a61375faa6f3","tid":1514361,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0da93ffded2514c812d5fce09904c40fc7b8416f","tid":1514361,"uid":60129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:00:17.000Z","msg":"屌 又要而家討論幾日後嘅事<br />\n<br />\n次次遊行次次討論<br />\n你討論完斬冇人跟嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n硬係唔可以比果日落場嘅人決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人地前線特登開個記招話連登係冷氣軍師 真係冇做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"話咗唔係公投 <br />\n但起碼出個時有心理準備 <br />\n會唔會中途就開波<br />\n<br />\n我都有出去好多次都叫冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家問吓意見都唔得<br />\n咁818全部人都係冷氣軍師了<br />\n<br />\n不過咁 多數都無不反對通知書架啦<br />\n所以個post廢廢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a0e5e5cb111b83ddc207c7896a228163e1a7dc","ti